         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">5/9/87 ¶  ¶ Only a few words this time, dear Prof. Bocage, to inform you, that I have sent  ¶ this day ¶  to the care of Mess. Watson &amp; Scull two cases for your museum by the Peninsular and Oriental S...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.09.05b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To José Barbosa du Bocage </p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Arquivo Histórico do Museu Bocage, Universidade de Lisboa, Lisbon.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Annotated:<seg style="color: #0904ff; "> but what does the annotation say?</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>5/9/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Only a few words this time, dear Prof. Bocage, to inform you, that I have sent <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">this day</hi>
               </seg> to the care of Mess. Watson &amp; Scull two cases for your museum by the Peninsular and Oriental Steamer just leaving. The one case contains the cask (small) with fishes &amp;c in methylized alcohol; the other case contains mainly bird-skins. Among the latter is a duplicate pair of Me[nu]ra superba.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>Superb lyrebird.</p>
               </note> Should the museum of Coimbra not already possess this beautiful bird, I would beg of you, to let one pair go to Coimbra. I will send soon more zoologic collections, also more dried plants for Count Ficalho.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With regardful remembrance</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your Ferd. von Mueller</p>
         </div>
      </body>
